name: No. 1 January 1, 2017

description:
Desperate to lose his virginity, Sou summons a devil named Kougure from the underworld to help with the deed. However, when he discovers that Kogure is a boy, he flees. Thinking the ordeal is over, Sou returns home only to find Kogure has insinuates himself into Sou’s life, and that he’s determined to stay until their deal is complete.

Desperate to figure out a way to nullify the agreement, Suo finds himself blocked by the devil at every turn. This stubborn Incubus is willing to do whatever it takes to win him over. But how will Sou handle a devil in his life?

Release Dates

  • Digital Edition - November 30, 2016
  • Print Edition - March 15, 2017
name: 1st Bite

description:
Welcome to Mizuryuland! In the future, a sex themed amusement park exists that caters to every desire anyone can think of. No limits are found in Mizuryuland where sexual freedom has a home.

In need of being cheered up, Mai is brought to the park with her two friends and she soon discovers it is a place to her to unleash her naught side. Mother and daughter team, Yumika and Ako both enjoy sex and find themselves at home in the park. Both are determined to have as much sex as possible! Sakiko is a chronic cheater and she finds that there is no hope for her, so she takes her friend’s advice that even women need to let loose every once in a while. And poor Akihiko finally gets his self-esteem up when he enters the animal park where he is invited to play with another man’s wife. Anything and everything kinky is delivered at Mizuryuland.
name: The 1st Day

description: In a far-off village, humans and yokai live side by side in peace. A young boy, Soichiro, often plays with Momiji, the daughter of the village oni. One day, Momiji takes Soichiro back to her house to play, but perhaps she also has something else in mind...
name: Vol. 1
